Darkfate/Shivah/Attilla::


Darkfate was flying towards the battle followed by Attilla and 
Shivah. He opened his comm link in Zardus's and Galvatron's 
Frecuencies. "Here's Darkfate" said the male "What's the situetion 
where you're in order to follow a good strategy."

While he wait answer he asked "Well Bloodstrike, Do you have a 
menssage of Zardus, some information... anything that could be 
usefull???"
